Christina PAYLAN, M.D., Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D19-0091 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. January 14, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The petition for writ of mandamus is denied. The petitioner's motion to expedite is denied as moot.

LaROSE, C.J., and SILBERMAN and NORTHCUTT, JJ., Concur.
